# 🔐 Password Strength Checker with Breach Lookup

A Python tool that helps users create stronger passwords by:
- ✅ Checking password length and complexity  
- ✅ Scoring overall strength (0–5 scale)  
- ✅ Checking against [HaveIBeenPwned](https://haveibeenpwned.com/) to see if the password has appeared in known data breaches  
- ✅ Providing actionable recommendations for improvement  

---

## 🚀 Features
- Detects uppercase, lowercase, numbers, and special characters  
- Ensures minimum recommended length (12+ characters)  
- Uses SHA-1 k-anonymity API model for secure breach checking  
- CLI-based, lightweight, and easy to run locally  

